data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the picturesque Valencia on the Lake community! This meticulously maintained 3 bed 3 bath home offers a spacious open floorplan perfect for both relaxed living and entertaining. The heart of the home is the large kitchen, complete with a center island that provides ample workspace and additional seating. The primary suite is a peaceful retreat, featuring an en-suite bathroom and plenty of closet space. Upstairs, you'll find a flex room with its own full bath and closet. This versatile space can serve as a fourth bedroom, family room, or whatever your needs might require.  The backyard is large with a covered patio. Residents enjoy access to a range of amenities, including a sparkling pool, a fully-equipped gym, and scenic walking trails. And for those who love the water, Lake Lewisville is just a stone's throw away, offering boating, fishing, and other recreational activities. Zoned for Little Elm ISD.
